There are 18 million posts on this board that explain, with 4 VERY SPECIFIC exceptions (Melody and Composition of Ervaj, and Warsong and Battlecry of the VahShir IIRC), Song Haste and Spell Haste do NOT stack.<br>
<br>
If you're on a raid, you're most likely getting Speed of the Shissar as your spell haste.  This 66% overwrites the haste portion of our epic, SO.....   if you have a CoF you are at 66+36 = 102% haste.   <p>&lt;br&gt;Keyeluke&lt;br&gt;<br>
